    "However, errors occurred when providing only the numerical result.",
    "This highlighted the need for a structured reasoning process, or \"chain of thought, \" to ensure accurate heading calculations.",
    "A new key, \"rationale\", was added to the JSON output to encourage reasoning before determining the final heading.",
    "Introducing the \"rationale\" key significantly improved flocking behavior.",
    "The agents demonstrated more consistent heading adjustments, enhancing the emergence of flocking dynamics."
